title: Aha-Soft Icon Software Collection Portable DC 23.07.2016
description:
Aha-Soft Icon Software Collection Portable DC 23.07.2016

About this release

These portable applications were created with VMWare ThinApp, compatible with any Windows version (XP and above, 32-bit/64-bit).
All applications are registered, shell extensions and file associations are disabled.

Just extract the archive and run one of these application

AhaView 4.52
Any to Icon 3.56
ArtCursors 5.27
ArtIcons Pro 5.48
Icon to Any 3.26
IconLover 5.44
IconXP 3.36
